"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1931960-olympics-denied-medal-penis-pole-vault\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  A French pole vaulter who missed out on the final at theParis Olympicsbecause of his penis has been urged to 'call a drag queen' by a former tennis star.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 155, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4, \"end\": 10, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9995402536589595, \"rank\": 0.00044747869527587253, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Anthony Ammirati sent the internet into a frenzy over the weekend when his manhood clipped the 5.70-metre bar, denying him a spot in Monday's final.\", \"from\": 157, \"to\": 305, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a bizarre moment, and now ex-professional tennis player and Serena Williams' former coach Rennae Stubbs has since weighed in on the incident.\", \"from\": 307, \"to\": 455, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 374, \"end\": 389, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serena_Williams\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Serena Williams\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serena_Williams\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serena_Williams\"}, {\"begin\": 404, \"end\": 417, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rennae_Stubbs\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rennae Stubbs\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rennae_Stubbs\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rennae_Stubbs\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Taking to social media to offer a tip to Ammirati,Stubbs commented: \\\"Seriously!!!\", \"from\": 457, \"to\": 538, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 507, \"end\": 513, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rennae_Stubbs\", \"score\": 0.9999994985270299, \"rank\": 5.009246696084442e-07, \"text\": \"Stubbs\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rennae_Stubbs\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rennae_Stubbs\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When your sport is all about getting your body over a bar and it's a matter of millimetres!\", \"from\": 539, \"to\": 630, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My man!\", \"from\": 632, \"to\": 640, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Call a drag queen!\", \"from\": 641, \"to\": 659, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She will teach u how to tuck it!\", \"from\": 660, \"to\": 692, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is unbelievable!\\\"\", \"from\": 693, \"to\": 715, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Stubbs was referencing a practice called 'tucking' adopted by drag queens, which sees the male genitals tucked between the legs and the buttocks - something which would have certainly helped Ammirati out in his event.\", \"from\": 717, \"to\": 934, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Among the memes and the online jibes, Ammirati has been dealing with the disappointment of his Olympic dream coming to an end early.\", \"from\": 936, \"to\": 1068, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the aftermath of the weekend mishap, Ammirati broke his silence on his exit from the competition, but the Frenchman did not directly reference his penis-related gaffe.\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1240, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pick up your ultimate guide to the Olympics!\", \"from\": 1242, \"to\": 1286, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Going for Gold provides the day-by-day rundown of what's on and when.\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1356, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Click here to buy.\", \"from\": 1357, \"to\": 1375, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking to the French Athletics Federation, Ammirati said: \\\"It's a big disappointment.\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1468, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1397, \"end\": 1424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Athletics_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French Athletics Federation\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Athletics_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Athletics_Federation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am a bit gutted, because I did not miss anything on the third attempt at 5.70 m.  \\\"What I did miss was a bit of jumping in training to fine-tune the settings.\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1629, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just a technical session.\", \"from\": 1630, \"to\": 1655, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He added: \\\"I was 100 per cent physically, but I was missing a bit of pole vault.\", \"from\": 1657, \"to\": 1737, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The conditions were good.\", \"from\": 1739, \"to\": 1765, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the first time I have started a competition without any stress.\", \"from\": 1766, \"to\": 1834, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not miss:Carlos Alcaraz cries and stops interview after losing Olympic gold to Djokovic  Do not miss:Team GB's Amber Rutter 'cheated out of Olympic gold' after controversial final  Do not miss:BBC viewers fume 'we are fed up' as Olympics coverage becomes 'insufferable'  \\\"As I was a total outsider, I only had one goal: to interact with the audience.\", \"from\": 1836, \"to\": 2189, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1848, \"end\": 1862, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\"}, {\"begin\": 1940, \"end\": 1947, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9936702033922664, \"rank\": 0.003283195243472192, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 2032, \"end\": 2035, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.9905311750560044, \"rank\": 0.009329981177608321, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was almost there.\\\"\", \"from\": 2190, \"to\": 2210, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thankfully for Ammirati, he wasn't the only pole vaulter to go viral over the weekend, with Estonian athlete Karel Tilga also enduring an afternoon to forget.\", \"from\": 2212, \"to\": 2370, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2304, \"end\": 2312, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Estonia\", \"score\": 0.7148488363085734, \"rank\": 0.3986649050892194, \"text\": \"Estonian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Estonia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Estonia\"}, {\"begin\": 2321, \"end\": 2332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karel_Tilga\", \"score\": 0.999999039552683, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Karel Tilga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karel_Tilga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karel_Tilga\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2372, \"to\": 2481, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2482, \"to\": 2558, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2559, \"to\": 2591, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  Unlike Ammirati, the 26-year-old did not come close to clearing the bar, instead, his pole got stuck in the floor with Tilga left dangling precariously in the air.\", \"from\": 2592, \"to\": 2779, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2735, \"end\": 2740, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tilga,_Tartu_County\", \"score\": 0.669467902590356, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tilga\", \"types\": [\"Q532\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tilga,_Tartu_County\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tilga,_Tartu_County\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tilga eventually came back down to earth, but it wasn't without a bang, as the Estonian crashed to the floor in a less-than-graceful heap.\", \"from\": 2781, \"to\": 2919, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2781, \"end\": 2786, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tilga,_Tartu_County\", \"score\": 0.669467902590356, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tilga\", \"types\": [\"Q532\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tilga,_Tartu_County\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tilga,_Tartu_County\"}, {\"begin\": 2860, \"end\": 2868, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Estonia\", \"score\": 0.7148488363085734, \"rank\": 0.3986649050892194, \"text\": \"Estonian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Estonia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Estonia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 2921, \"to\": 3090, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3058, \"end\": 3071, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.108903075725576e-20, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 3092, \"to\": 3159, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3107,